 la publicité. L'ouvrage est donc à la fois un pamphlet et un livre-ressource.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aAdvertisingxSocial aspects. 0aDeceptive advertising. 0aManipulative behavior. 0aPersuasion (Psychology). 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Communication Studies.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763703244?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763703244423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763703244/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles